### 获取商品信息
GET http://localhost:8000/goods/goods_retrieve/3/


### 创建商品
POST http://localhost:8000/goods/goods_create/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test",
  "price": 9999.00,
  "number": 100,
  "desc": "这是最新出的iphone 17 pro max",
  "status": "pending",
  "sold_count": 12
}

### 修改商品
PUT http://localhost:8000/goods/goods_retrieve/2/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iqoo 15",
  "price": 4499.00,
  "number": 2001,
  "desc": "这是最新出的iqoo 15",
  "status": "normal",
  "sold_count": 1200
}

### 删除商品
DELETE http://localhost:8000/goods/goods_retrieve/3/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}